767
01:21:53,850 --> 01:21:55,200
Bog vas klanja vasim zavestanjima.

768
01:21:55,400 --> 01:21:57,612
Kako mozete raditi stvari koje ste ucinili?

769
01:22:04,463 --> 01:22:06,222
Moji stari veruju u "Young Kwai-Chai"(Rast djavolskog deteta)

770
01:22:06,322 --> 01:22:08,769
"Rast djavoljeg deteta"

771
01:22:09,410 --> 01:22:10,870
